# Backup Scripts & Policies

This directory includes backup policies, rotation strategies, and automation scripts for both Windows and Linux environments.

## Contents

- `rsync-weekly-job.sh`: Bash script for automated weekly Linux backups using rsync.
- `backup-policy-overview.md`: Describes rotation strategies (GFS, 3-2-1), frequency, storage, and encryption best practices.

## Use Cases

- Backup automation and planning
- Compliance and redundancy
- Hands-on scripting demonstration
